Yue...

00:05:42.466 --> 00:05:43.466
Jin...

00:05:45.507 --> 00:05:47.986
Zhao!

00:05:49.266 --> 00:05:49.986
¿Qué?

00:05:50.186 --> 00:05:51.027
¿Por qué me pellizcaste?

00:05:51.572 --> 00:05:52.806
