00:11:27.427 --> 00:11:28.586
Es todo tuyo.

00:11:29.586 --> 00:11:31.187
¿Por qué eres tan generosa hoy?

00:11:38.747 --> 00:11:39.666
Yue Jin Zhao,

00:11:39.666 --> 00:11:40.586
